Package: scTools
Type: Package
Title: Tools to help with analysis of single-cell transcriptome datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jordi Camps
Maintainer: Jordi Camps <jordi.camps@kuleuven.be>
Description: Handy functions to make final analysis much easier. Contains extraction of principal components, plotting of PCA plots, heatmaps, clusterings and saving the images in designated folders.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports: ggplot2, dplyr, igraph, reshape2, tibble, tidyr, viridis
